sequenceDiagram
  participant CLI as CLI task-pull runner
  participant API as Server-agent task-pull API
  participant Job as ServerExecutionJob
  participant Sync as Linked-run finish sync
  participant Docs as Progress and verification evidence

  CLI->>API: contract(identity)
  API-->>CLI: default-off gates and lifecycle support
  CLI->>API: claim(identity)
  API->>Job: claim queued server_agent job
  API-->>CLI: safe task payload
  loop command execution
    CLI->>API: ack(progress)
    API->>Job: renew matching running lock
  end
  CLI->>API: finish(terminal status, logs, result)
  API->>Job: write terminal outcome for matching lock owner
  API->>Sync: sync linked business run after finish
  API-->>CLI: finish metadata and job sample
  Docs->>Docs: record verification logs and remaining gaps
